Usage: <main class> [options]  Options:
  * -f, --format    Message format (e.g. tcpgelf)
    -h, --help      Show usage information and exit
                    Default: false
  * -x, --host      Target host
  * -p, --port      Target port
                    Default: 0
    -d, --sleep     Delay between each message that is sent in milliseconds (per
                    thread). Default: 5
                    Default: 5
    -t, --threads   Number of parallel threads to use
                    Default: 1

